# 🏦 Bankora - Banking Management System (BMS)

A scalable, secure, and production-grade **Fullstack Banking Management System** built using modern backend and frontend architecture principles.

This project simulates a real-world digital banking platform including customer dashboard, admin panel, secure transactions, and scalable backend services.

---

# 🚀 Overview

The Banking Management System (BMS) provides:

## 👤 Customer Features

* User Registration & Login
* KYC Submission
* Dashboard with Account Overview
* Deposit / Withdraw / Transfer Funds
* Transaction History
* Loan Application & EMI Tracking
* Real-time Notifications

## 👨‍💼 Admin Features

* Approve / Reject KYC
* Freeze / Unfreeze Accounts
* Monitor Transactions
* View System Metrics Dashboard

---

# 🏗 System Architecture

## High-Level Architecture

Frontend (Next.js)
↓
API Gateway
↓
Microservices
↓
Database / Cache / Message Broker

---

# 🖥 Frontend Architecture

## Tech Stack (Frontend)

* **Framework:** Next.js (App Router)
* **Language:** TypeScript
* **State Management:** Redux Toolkit / Zustand
* **UI Library:** TailwindCSS / ShadCN UI
* **Authentication:** JWT (HTTP-only cookies)
* **API Communication:** Axios / Fetch

## Frontend Modules

* Authentication Pages (Login / Register)
* Customer Dashboard
* Transfer Money Page
* Transaction History Page
* Loan Management Page
* Admin Dashboard
* KYC Management Panel

## Frontend Folder Structure

```
frontend/
│
├── app/
│   ├── login/
│   ├── register/
│   ├── dashboard/
│   ├── transfer/
│   ├── transactions/
│   ├── loans/
│   └── admin/
│
├── components/
├── services/
├── store/
├── hooks/
└── utils/
```

